<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 20:07:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“哈马斯无法统治加沙：”欧盟主席提出以色列与哈马斯战争后的路线图</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-06/ty-article/hamas-cannot-govern-gaza-eu-chief-presents-roadmap-for-after-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-a5bf-d9c0-a5fb-edff13d10000</link><description>乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩表示，以色列与哈马斯战争结束后的道路可能包括一支“联合国授权的国际和平部队”，并呼吁立即释放加沙的所有人质</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 19:32:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-06/ty-article/hamas-cannot-govern-gaza-eu-chief-presents-roadmap-for-after-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-a5bf-d9c0-a5fb-edff13d10000</guid></item><item><title>叶史瓦大学向受到反犹太主义威胁的教授提供职位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/yeshiva-university-to-offer-positions-to-professors-threatened-by-antisemitism/0000018b-a5b9-da24-a1cb-b7fd5b830000</link><description>纽约叶史瓦大学商学院院长向美国的犹太和以色列教授发出呼吁，他们发现自己处于“敌对环境”中，可能有兴趣访问教职至少一个学期</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 18:11:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/yeshiva-university-to-offer-positions-to-professors-threatened-by-antisemitism/0000018b-a5b9-da24-a1cb-b7fd5b830000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的极右翼部长是给哈马斯的礼物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-06/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-far-right-ministers-are-a-gift-to-hamas/0000018b-a5bc-dc0b-a1cb-e5fe57210000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡知道，他的极右翼部长（其中一些人将核弹作为加沙的“选择”）对以色列不利。但一如既往，他将自己的政治需要和个人利益置于任何其他考虑之上</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 18:09:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-06/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-far-right-ministers-are-a-gift-to-hamas/0000018b-a5bc-dc0b-a1cb-e5fe57210000</guid></item><item><title>德国记者被以色列士兵拘留：“用枪指着我们并问我们是否是犹太人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/german-journalists-detained-by-israeli-soldiers-asked-if-we-were-jewish-at-gunpoint/0000018b-a5ae-d9c0-a5fb-edfee9ed0000</link><description>士兵们在西岸希伯伦以南拘留了德国公共广播公司 ARD 的记者，该团队正在报道极端主义定居者的暴力行为。以色列军队：“以色列国防军对造成的任何不便表示歉意”</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 18:04:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/german-journalists-detained-by-israeli-soldiers-asked-if-we-were-jewish-at-gunpoint/0000018b-a5ae-d9c0-a5fb-edfee9ed0000</guid></item><item><title>“这非常个人化”：10 月 7 日，以色列士兵在加沙内部生活发生了改变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-06/ty-article-podcast/its-very-personal-inside-gaza-with-the-israeli-soldiers-whose-lives-changed-on-oct-7/0000018b-a559-d9c0-a5fb-ed59e9f20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 17:21:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-06/ty-article-podcast/its-very-personal-inside-gaza-with-the-israeli-soldiers-whose-lives-changed-on-oct-7/0000018b-a559-d9c0-a5fb-ed59e9f20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称在约旦河西岸击毙了四名恐怖分子，其中包括哈马斯和法塔赫成员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-killed-four-terrorists-including-hamas-fatah-members-in-west-bank/0000018b-a580-dc0b-a1cb-e5c681d30000</link><description>据以色列称，两名被杀的哈马斯和法塔赫成员制造了数十起枪击袭击事件，并计划在以色列境内进行更多袭击</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 17:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-killed-four-terrorists-including-hamas-fatah-members-in-west-bank/0000018b-a580-dc0b-a1cb-e5c681d30000</guid></item><item><title>作家指责以色列在加沙实施“种族灭绝”后，耶路撒冷顶级剧院冻结了演出</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/top-jerusalem-theater-freezes-production-after-writer-accuses-israel-of-genocide-in-gaza/0000018b-a584-dc0b-a1cb-e5c655550000</link><description>英国裔阿富汗人哈米德·阿米里（Hamed Amiri）在社交媒体上发布了反对以色列的言论，他撰写了戏剧《有两颗心的男孩》的回忆录。可汗剧院表示避免艺术审查，但不会容忍“煽动”恐怖主义</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 16:59:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/top-jerusalem-theater-freezes-production-after-writer-accuses-israel-of-genocide-in-gaza/0000018b-a584-dc0b-a1cb-e5c655550000</guid></item><item><title>德国媒体敦促在加沙战争期间坚定支持以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/german-language-press-urges-unwavering-support-for-israel-during-gaza-war/0000018b-a4be-dc41-af9f-efbe19e20000</link><description>在以色列和哈马斯之间的战争尚未结束的情况下，面对越来越大规模的要求停火的集会，德国、奥地利和瑞士媒体形成统一战线，敦促加大对以色列的支持</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 16:37:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/german-language-press-urges-unwavering-support-for-israel-during-gaza-war/0000018b-a4be-dc41-af9f-efbe19e20000</guid></item><item><title>加沙哈马斯卫生部：自战争开始以来已有逾万人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-health-ministry-in-gaza-more-than-10-000-have-been-killed-there-since-the-war-began/0000018b-a541-da24-a1cb-b74d53b40000</link><description>据该部称，70%以上的死者是妇女、儿童和老人；超过24,000人受伤；医生被迫在没有麻醉的情况下进行手术</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 16:27:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-health-ministry-in-gaza-more-than-10-000-have-been-killed-there-since-the-war-began/0000018b-a541-da24-a1cb-b74d53b40000</guid></item><item><title>南非召回驻特拉维夫特使，指责以色列在加沙实施“种族灭绝”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2023-11-06/ty-article/south-africa-recalls-ambassador-in-tel-aviv-over-israeli-genocide-in-gaza/0000018b-a528-dc0b-a1cb-e5eeab060000</link><description>比勒陀利亚还威胁要对以色列大使采取行动，因为他批评以色列对战争的立场。南非与约旦、土耳其、玻利维亚和智利等其他国家一起对以色列采取类似的外交行动</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 16:18:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2023-11-06/ty-article/south-africa-recalls-ambassador-in-tel-aviv-over-israeli-genocide-in-gaza/0000018b-a528-dc0b-a1cb-e5eeab060000</guid></item><item><title>欧洲野猫冷落家猫2000年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2023-11-06/ty-article/wildcats-in-europe-snubbed-domestic-cats-for-2-000-years/0000018b-a516-d9c0-a5fb-ed5e1e760000</link><description>直到 20 世纪 50 年代，苏格兰野猫队也一直坚守着抵抗入侵者的立场，那么后来发生了什么变化呢？</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 16:00:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2023-11-06/ty-article/wildcats-in-europe-snubbed-domestic-cats-for-2-000-years/0000018b-a516-d9c0-a5fb-ed5e1e760000</guid></item><item><title>35个以色列犹太和阿拉伯权利团体呼吁停火、人质交易、政治解决冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-human-rights-orgs-call-for-ceasefire-hostage-deal-political-solution-to-conflict/0000018b-a53a-da24-a1cb-b77e8a860000</link><description>这些组织签署的一封公开信还呼吁以色列遏制西岸猖獗的定居者暴力，停止迫害以色列的巴勒斯坦公民以及那些声援加沙居民并反对战争的人</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 15:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-human-rights-orgs-call-for-ceasefire-hostage-deal-political-solution-to-conflict/0000018b-a53a-da24-a1cb-b77e8a860000</guid></item><item><title>这些是伊朗从也门向以色列发射的导弹和无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-iranian-rockets-and-drones-launched-at-israel-from-yemen/0000018b-a45b-dc41-af9f-ef7bcc800000</link><description>以色列、美国甚至沙特都在红海地区部署导弹防御系统，以挫败伊朗支持的也门胡塞政权的袭击</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 15:44:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-iranian-rockets-and-drones-launched-at-israel-from-yemen/0000018b-a45b-dc41-af9f-ef7bcc800000</guid></item><item><title>支持乌克兰？然后支持以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/support-ukraine-then-support-israel/0000018b-a4dd-da24-a1cb-b7ddf6f30000</link><description>乌克兰和以色列都面临着具有明显种族灭绝意图、使用恐怖主义和犯下危害人类罪的敌人。简而言之，如果俄罗斯获胜，乌克兰人就会消失。如果哈马斯获胜，以色列人就会消失</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 15:33:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/support-ukraine-then-support-israel/0000018b-a4dd-da24-a1cb-b7ddf6f30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境警察在耶路撒冷持刀袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-border-police-officer-killed-in-jerusalem-stabbing-attack/0000018b-a515-dc41-af9f-ef37ec410000</link><description>这名女警官与另一名中度受伤的警官被送往医院，情况危急，随后被宣布死亡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 15:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-border-police-officer-killed-in-jerusalem-stabbing-attack/0000018b-a515-dc41-af9f-ef37ec410000</guid></item><item><title>父母得知，据信死亡的以色列儿童被关押在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/israeli-child-believed-dead-is-being-held-in-gaza-parents-learn/0000018b-a472-d831-a3ef-acf235010000</link><description>10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀后，8 岁的以色列和爱尔兰公民艾米丽·汉德 (Emily Hand) 的家人为她哀悼。周末，他们得知她还活着，并且被哈马斯关押在加沙</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 15:08:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/israeli-child-believed-dead-is-being-held-in-gaza-parents-learn/0000018b-a472-d831-a3ef-acf235010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长暂停要求大学报告处理涉嫌支持恐怖主义的学生的命令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/minister-suspends-order-for-universities-to-report-handling-terror-supporting-students/0000018b-a461-dc0b-a1cb-e5e76f4b0000</link><description>大学校长反对这项命令，要求他们报告对据称以恐怖方式表示支持的学生的处理情况，称这“为学生之间的举报和冲突打开了大门”。周一，教育部长宣布该指令现已暂停</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 15:01:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/minister-suspends-order-for-universities-to-report-handling-terror-supporting-students/0000018b-a461-dc0b-a1cb-e5e76f4b0000</guid></item><item><title>两名加沙劳工在以色列拘留期间死亡，军队未展开调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/two-gazan-laborers-die-in-israeli-custody-army-fails-to-open-investigation/0000018b-a4d2-d9c0-a5fb-edda0c250000</link><description>这些工人被关押在两个不同的军营，与其他数千人一起被关押在战争开始时，他们在以色列工作的许可证被取消。其中一人请求医疗援助；军队没有报告死亡人数</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 14:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article/.premium/two-gazan-laborers-die-in-israeli-custody-army-fails-to-open-investigation/0000018b-a4d2-d9c0-a5fb-edda0c250000</guid></item><item><title>解释：谁是也门胡塞武装？他们为何攻击以色列？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-who-are-the-houthis-and-why-are-they-attacking-israel/0000018b-a4da-da24-a1cb-b7de6c5f0000</link><description>尽管位于以色列以南 2000 公里处，胡塞运动目前已向度假城市埃拉特发动了三起单独的袭击。专家解释了为什么这符合其更广泛的反以色列、反犹太议程，以及为什么它更像是其伊朗赞助人的合作伙伴而不是代理人</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 14:45:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-who-are-the-houthis-and-why-are-they-attacking-israel/0000018b-a4da-da24-a1cb-b7de6c5f0000</guid></item><item><title>“我希望我被绑架的妹妹不要放弃，尽管这一定是一场噩梦”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article-magazine/i-hope-my-kidnapped-sister-doesnt-give-up-even-though-it-has-to-be-a-nightmare/0000018b-a483-dc41-af9f-efa3f7c30000</link><description>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列家庭：一个特别项目 ■ Moran Yanai 被绑架时正在诺瓦节上出售她手工制作的珠宝。她的姐姐和哥哥现在想象她在哈马斯的地道里拥抱一个小孩</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 12:42:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-06/ty-article-magazine/i-hope-my-kidnapped-sister-doesnt-give-up-even-though-it-has-to-be-a-nightmare/0000018b-a483-dc41-af9f-efa3f7c30000</guid></item></channel></rss>